    },
    "shortDescription": "<p>You place a drop of your blood on a weapon and charge it with magic so that you transfer a small amount of your life essence to the next living creature you strike with the weapon. Thereafter, you can spend a move action to know the direction and general distance of that creature. The target can negate this effect with a successful Will save. You must strike a creature within 1 minute of casting this spell or the magic is wasted, but once the Mark of Blood takes effect it is permanent until dispelled or removed via an effect like <i>remove curse</i>.</p>"
